704582f-a.title: Brooklyn: Fulton Street - New Jersey Avenue
704582f-a.text:
Fulton Street, at the N.W. corner of New Jersey Ave., showing the home
of John S. Andrews in 1873. (This house originally stood on the east side
of Pennsylvania Ave., between Fulton Street and Jamaica Ave).
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
